metadata.name: Salvation
metadata.description:
I thought I was helping people without compensation, but in the back of my mind I subconsciously want something in return. I don't want these fake wings anymore. I want to be saved too.

･2628×3641pix
･The winner of this auction get the original psd file.
Airdrop stamps are available to those who participate in the auction.


無償で人助けをしていたつもりだけど、心の奥では無意識に見返りを求めてしまっているんだ。こんな見せかけだけの羽はもういらない。私だって救われたい。
